        <note>Title from incipit (f. 1r).</note>
        <note>Written in 9-10 lines per leaf.</note>
        <note>6 leaves foliated 1-6, upper left and lower right verso.</note>
        <note>Mistakes blacked out; some corrections and additions in margins; vertical margins marked with double red line.</note>
        <note>Partial watermark on final folio including the letters N and B, the roman numeral VII, and possible parts of animals.</note>
